Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.61,0:29:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the shocking flight of  mother Tamiko from home,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.19,0:29:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,comes the apparition of a Time Patroller, Bunmei Muruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.11,0:29:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will discover what is "the principle\Nof non-intervention in history,"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.82,0:29:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what is the crime'of "improper\Npersonal relation with relatives."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.79,0:29:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time! Gosenzosama Banbanzai, episode 2:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.46,0:29:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banquet With No Holds Barred.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.33,0:29:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you next time!
